Stelios Becomes Chief Executive of Easycar, Sunday Times Says

-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 
2011-06-26T07:50:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-26/stelios-becomes-chief-executive-of-easycar-sunday-times-says.html
Stelios Haji-Ioannou appointed
himself acting chief executive officer of Easycar Ltd., the
 Sunday Times  said, without saying where it got the information.  The move follows the departure of three directors in the
last year and as the company cuts costs, the London-based
newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ben Martin in London at 
